oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Eugene Cernan on the Moon
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Cernan, Eugene; astronauts; space travel; portraits;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Autographed photograph of Eugene Cernan, "the last man on the Moon." At the top, Cernan wrote "Apollo XVII on the Moon - Dec 1972." At the bottom, he wrote "To Mrs. Phoebe F. Omlie - With My Warm Best Wishes -- Gene Cernan." Included is part of the envelope in which the photograph was sent from NASA in Houston.
